      • AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings

        public AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings(AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings.AdaptiveBitrateControlMode mode,
                              int minimumBitrate,
                              int maximumBitrate,
                              int flushBufferThreshold,
                              int minimumFramerate)
        Creates a new AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings object with the specified mode and settings.
        Parameters:
        mode - The AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings.AdaptiveBitrateControlMode to use for reducing bitrate.
        minimumBitrate - Minimum bitrate. Values in kbps: 50000 - 10000000 (10Mbps)
        flushBufferThreshold - If the change of bitrate is above this threshold, the buffer will be flushed and samples discarded. Values in percent: 0 - 100.
        minimumFramerate - Minimum framerate. Values in frames per second: 5 - 60.

      • AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings

        public AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings(AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings.AdaptiveBitrateControlMode mode,
                              int minimumBitrate,
                              int maximumBitrate,
                              int flushBufferThreshold,
                              int minimumFramerate,
                              boolean enableAudioABC)
        Creates a new AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings object with the specified mode and settings.
        Parameters:
        mode - The AdaptiveBitrateControlSettings.AdaptiveBitrateControlMode to use for reducing bitrate.
        minimumBitrate - Minimum bitrate. Values in kbps: 50000 - 10000000 (10Mbps)
        flushBufferThreshold - If the change of bitrate is above this threshold, the buffer will be flushed and samples discarded. Values in percent: 0 - 100.
        minimumFramerate - Minimum framerate. Values in frames per second: 5 - 60.
        enableAudioABC - Enable Adaptive Bitrate Controll for audio.
